        <headline>Heat Advisory issued July 28 at 6:22AM EDT until July 28 at 8:00PM EDT by NWS Blacksburg VA</headline>
        <description>* WHAT...Heat index values up to 106 expected.

* WHERE...In North Carolina, Caswell and Rockingham Counties. In
Virginia, Charlotte, Halifax, and Pittsylvania Counties.

* WHEN...From noon today to 8 PM EDT this evening.

* IMPACTS...Hot temperatures and high humidity may cause heat
illnesses.
</description>
        <instruction>Drink plenty of fluids, stay in an air-conditioned room, stay out of
the sun, and check up on relatives and neighbors.</instruction>
